description:
Support and Capacity Development for Ministry of Foreign Trade in the UAE in the following areas:
. Negotiations
. WTO
. Policy Advise 
. Databases and ICT
. Mapping & Reporting 
. Workshops

subproject.corporate outcome: Public Sector Reform, including: enhancement of service delivery and resource management at the federal and emirate level.
subproject.description: The project aims to support the efforts of the Ministry of Foreign Trade in the UAE to build the capacities of its national experts and personnel in various sectors and to strengthen its negotiation skills and capacity in the area of foreign trade and with regards to WTO treaties and agreements that the state has ratified or signed
subproject.gender code: No noticeable contribution to gender equality
subproject.title: Support & Capacity development
